title: Starving Student Movers
name: Starving Student Movers
description: If you are moving across town, across the street, or within the same building our friendly, courteous movers will take good care of your treasured belongings. We will make every effort to ensure your needs are met and see to it that you are completely satisfied. Local moves are charged on an hourly basis. Our services include moving pads, wardrobe boxes, and basic insurance coverage. Additionally, we provide special handling to protect antiques and pianos.
